{"tid":256374,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台中台南行程問題","createTime":"2017-05-24T13:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T06:06:47.000Z","uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e370d8871aa41102a4c697318d23a5ffd350a8d7","tid":256374,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"Day1 桃園&gt;高雄<br />\nDay2,3 高雄&gt;墾丁<br />\nDay4 墾丁&gt;嘉義<br />\nDay5,6 台中<br />\nDay7,8 台北<br />\n<br />\n因為桃園入桃園出，所以盡量將最後兩日安排返係台北<br />\n其他大致上有冇咩技術上既問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我驚交通上會唔太方便，因為2個人去唔會考慮包車<br />\n咁多位安答有冇其他建議？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42756a16f0b379109551476a606098359ada89d","tid":256374,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"點解唔高雄去台北走？"},{"pid":"1ca62a1567274eb9f8d71526cb2745f397ac4da4","tid":256374,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"仲有話去台南但係行程無台南嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a844d8bf15203ab03ff46547e45d16c7855e8500","tid":256374,"uid":17570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有話去台南但係行程無台南嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係南部 唔係台南<br />\n好早買左機票 無open jet<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5565dd61ef78b8bec3b63eb55c53a94ef8b48e5b","tid":256374,"uid":74789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:44:18.000Z","msg":"你考慮下景點交通好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba25faabbeffdbb1ca992ca475bb753a1773bd58","tid":256374,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T17:51:46.000Z","msg":"樓主，認真提議你問下機票可否改高/南入北出，<br />\n錢事少，交通時間真係會花多好多。<br />\n<br />\n長時間係鐵路/自駕你亦都辛苦。"},{"pid":"d6501fb525fce4de3611df098c6ba15079caa9f8","tid":256374,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T17:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主，認真提議你問下機票可否改高/南入北出，<br />\n錢事少，交通時間真係會花多好多。<br />\n<br />\n長時間係鐵路/自駕你亦都辛苦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果補既錢唔係太大<br />\n比起你其他方法由北去南可能仲慳返少少<br />\n高鐵唔係平架都"},{"pid":"c0c577e4f6cdfe37375e2e4cd776de3033990633","tid":256374,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主，認真提議你問下機票可否改高/南入北出，<br />\n錢事少，交通時間真係會花多好多。<br />\n<br />\n長時間係鐵路/自駕你亦都辛苦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果補既錢唔係太大<br />\n比起你其他方法由北去南可能仲慳返少少<br />\n高鐵唔係平架都</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假如可以改高雄入台北出<br />\n<br />\nDay1 <del>桃園&gt;高雄</del>　高雄＞下飛機直奔墾丁<br />\nDay2,3 <del>高雄&gt;</del> 墾丁＞高雄 (留一晚)<br />\nDay4 <del>墾丁</del> 高雄&gt;嘉義<br />\nDay5,6 台中<br />\nDay7,8 台北<br />\n<br />\n台中去台北如果坐台鐵大約2.5-3小時<br />\n早幾日買定飛否則有機會冇位坐<br />\n(桃園開始多人上車，如果唔可以全段都俾到位你，你變左由台中企到台北)"},{"pid":"ef71cae15422725c8d999a3263b89272160baa08","tid":256374,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"如果你去嘉義唔係為咗阿里山嘅話喺臺南留日好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1288af505f19137f59b197202e277a1e8ee429","tid":256374,"uid":56912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:06:47.000Z","msg":"你去遊車河架?"}]}